---
// P - Drums & Vocals - African American intellectual
// Superpower: The Cerebral Beat - drumming so intellectual it generates equations and enlightenment
---

<div class="character p-char">
  <div class="power-effects">
    <span class="equation eq1">E=mc&sup2;</span>
    <span class="equation eq2">&pi;r&sup2;</span>
    <span class="equation eq3">&radic;2</span>
    <span class="equation eq4">&Sigma;f(x)</span>
    <span class="equation eq5">&infin;</span>
    <span class="equation eq6">&Delta;t</span>
    <span class="equation eq7">&#966;</span>
    <div class="brain-wave bw1"></div>
    <div class="brain-wave bw2"></div>
    <div class="brain-wave bw3"></div>
    <div class="enlighten-glow"></div>
  </div>
  <img src="/p.png" alt="P - Drums & Vocals" class="char-img" />
  <div class="char-name">P</div>
  <div class="char-power">The Cerebral Beat</div>
  <div class="char-desc">Drumming so intellectual it solves quantum equations mid-fill. The rhythm is the proof.</div>
</div>

<style>
  .p-char {
    position: relative;
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 320px;
  }

  .char-img {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 280px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    filter: drop-shadow(3px 3px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.2));
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .char-name {
    font-family: var(--comic);
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    color: var(--brown);
    letter-spacing: 4px;
    text-shadow: 2px 2px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
    margin-top: 0.25rem;
  }

  .char-power {
    font-family: var(--comic);
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: #2c2c54;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .char-desc {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    opacity: 0.7;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    max-width: 260px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .power-effects {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 3;
  }

  .equation {
    position: absolute;
    font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: #2c2c54;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: equationFloat 5s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  .eq1 { left: 0%; top: 10%; animation-delay: 0s; font-size: 1.1rem; }
  .eq2 { right: 2%; top: 20%; animation-delay: 0.7s; }
  .eq3 { left: 5%; top: 35%; animation-delay: 1.4s; font-size: 1.3rem; }
  .eq4 { right: 0%; top: 45%; animation-delay: 2.1s; font-size: 0.9rem; }
  .eq5 { left: 8%; top: 5%; animation-delay: 2.8s; font-size: 1.5rem; }
  .eq6 { right: 8%; top: 8%; animation-delay: 3.5s; }
  .eq7 { left: 2%; top: 25%; animation-delay: 4.2s; font-size: 1.4rem; }

  @keyframes equationFloat {
    0% { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px) scale(0.7); }
    10% { opacity: 0.7; transform: translateY(0) scale(1); }
    40% { opacity: 0.7; }
    50% { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-30px) scale(1.1); }
    100% { opacity: 0; }
  }

  .brain-wave {
    position: absolute;
    left: 50%;
    top: 12%;
    width: 30px;
    height: 30px;
    border: 2px solid #9b59b6;
    border-radius: 50%;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: brainPulse 3s ease-out infinite;
  }

  .bw2 { animation-delay: 1s; }
  .bw3 { animation-delay: 2s; }

  @keyframes brainPulse {
    0% { transform: translate(-50%, 0) scale(0.3); opacity: 0.6; }
    100% { transform: translate(-50%, 0) scale(5); opacity: 0; }
  }

  .enlighten-glow {
    position: absolute;
    left: 50%;
    top: 8%;
    width: 80px;
    height: 80px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(155, 89, 182, 0.2) 0%, transparent 70%);
    border-radius: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    animation: glowPulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  @keyframes glowPulse {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 0.5; transform: translateX(-50%) scale(1); }
    50% { opacity: 1; transform: translateX(-50%) scale(1.3); }
  }
</style>
